
LDAP Kit To-Do List
===================

   General
   -------
   * IPv6 Support: LKLdap and LKMessage needs to be updated to properly
     process IPv6 addresses if an IPv6 address is specified as the host or
     in the LDAP URL.
   * Remove custom error codes from LKError and replace with equivalent internal
     LDAP error codes.

   LDAP Opeartions
   ---------------
   * Add LDAP delete methods to LKLdap and LKMessage.
   * Add LDAP modify methods to LKLdap and LKMessage.
   * Add LDAP rename methods to LKLdap and LKMessage.
   * Add LDAP URL parse methods to LKLdap.
   * Add LDAP whoami  methods to LKLdap and LKMessage.

   Documentation
   -------------
   * Finish README.
   * Finish documenting source code with appledoc tags.
   * Publish LDAP Kit docsets to github webpage.

